Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A journey from which you can never return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasures that you can never again acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your very life, which once lost will never be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly all things in this world\Nwill never go back to the way they once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,people still continue, even today,\Nto get up and take another step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Spurred on by the thought of viewing\Na landscape they've never seen before,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they keep on walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A longing for the unknown, you see,\Nis something not a single soul is capable of stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, that was pretty amazing, Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the opponent's own special ability against it\Nlike that was a brilliant strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd come with us\Nto the bottom of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to ask of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can ask anything of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be, but it truly is a hard thing to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please kill Mitty for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, unable to resist, goes down in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Make those eyes shine brighter than a torch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The destination we are aiming for is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We squarely lose our way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of the open-mouthed netherworld
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chase the traces of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If an answer can be found now, we don't mind losing it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The echo is still reverberating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we do not part with that voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is always
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the yearning stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like, "I'm gonna sleep - just for two hours."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His belly button looks like it hurts,\Nbut it doesn't appear he's been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he must be like this 'cause he fired that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally I have found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's the bottom of this world, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,would like to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's hurry over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You stink... Don't stand so close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he's a cave raider from the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I believe it is time for a new approach\Nthat's free from the influence of conventional wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From the chief territory of the far north, Sereny...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in search of children suitable\Nfor forging a path to the netherworld's next era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Bondrewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cave raider of the Abyss and a White Whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave children, who do not falter even at the prospect\Nof setting foot inside the chasm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,please, take a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's give it a shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't keep company with idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not the only ones, then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, come and board the vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not, for my team of cave raiders\Nwill escort you throughout the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your destination is at a depth of around 13,000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There, in the depths' fifth layer, the Sea of Corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,lies the netherworld's forward operating base,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,where we strive to unravel\Nthe final mysteries of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This tastes so bland...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A White Whistle, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Being a White Whistle sure would be great, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we've got ourselves\Nan amazing chance here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was fine with whatever\Nas long as I could come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Before coming here, I'd go to garbage dumps\Nand pick out the least disgusting stuff to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else resorted to stealing or\Nbegging while singing songs on the streets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... didn't have the talent for anything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great skill to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing but treasures to pick up down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, if you're fine with whatever,\Nthen be my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mitty! A future White Whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm Nanachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee! Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, "Capital of the Unreturned."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can read nether glyphs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The only books found in the garbage\Nare the ones other people can't read, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to pronounce nether glyphs has been lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so pronunciations from our official language\Nare used in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple once you get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that was a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, let's go check it out together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you climb more than 10 meters,\Nyou'll be hit with the strains of ascending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, let me show you to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so what's the Abyssal Faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... To put in a nutshell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,When a life is lost in the Abyss,\Nthe soul is said to return to the bottom of this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the soul changes form and departs\Non a journey to someone who has wished for life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This very pit, the bottom of which\Nis still unknown, replaces God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose it's just kind of a source of comfort\Nand support that cave raiders rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, you're pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my partner for you!\NYou're the brains of our team!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're good at drawing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ilim...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,please come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it's Ilim's turn, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I get to go out there soon, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are certainly a lot fewer of us here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it'd be great if the two of us\Nare able to go out there together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After today's medical checkup,\Nlet's go on a little walk outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bondrewd, take me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait your turn, Nanachi.\NNo need to be impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sovereign of Dawn!\NWhat in the world are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing so many people\Ndown to the fifth layer like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even children from overseas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bring this up only now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It is also for this very purpose that I advocated\Nto have Black Whistles enter the fifth layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be different if they were cave raiders,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but taking children, who'll never be able to return\Ngiven the strain of doing so, is simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from a humane perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, then there is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For I am not making use of them as humans, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,MITTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What perfect timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, it is your turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That elevator is capable of quickly going\Nto the depths' sixth layer just below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Although its destination is no more than a dead end...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it is just the perfect depth for testing out\Na number of things, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my own miniature garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The sixth layer's Curse:\N"Death, or loss of one's humanity"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sure like to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Those chambers you are in\Nare capable of forcing the Curse all to one side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempts were made that paired a person with something\Nbesides a fellow human, but they didn't go well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Nanachi just happened to come join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret having to use two cute,\Nlittle beings such as yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as you two are such close friends,\NI'm sure this will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying... you tricked us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavens no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The result of this research will give birth to the hint\Nneeded to drive the darkness from this chasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be thanks to all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, you will be on the side to which the Curse is driven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best to endure it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die partway through,\Nyour partner will also be hit with the Curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. It's alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll endure this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I end up not being human anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,let my soul return to you, Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,MITTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! It hurts so bad!\NGod... please save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I... finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty! Mitty!\NI... finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a treasure I hold dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.13,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!\NPlease...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't take her away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,PLEASE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, how very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you are truly wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as usual, I see you're drawing\Ninstead of helping with the research...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I now understand the "curse" that Mitty received.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a wonderful result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For it to produce such a byproduct,\Nthe Abyss truly is astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Curse, which she received twofold,\Ndid not just cause the loss of her humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but also made her incapable of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Her limbs, which should have been mashed up,\Nhave started to grow back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,While this is now the ninth time she's been resurrected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the only change is that her form becomes\Nslightly more distorted each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, I'm sorry for running away like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't just let him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,keep doing as he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll figure something out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Mitty, it's a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same one that was screeching\Nback then, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to your liking? Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I try using, she just suffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for forcing you to stay alive for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put you out of your misery now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A way to kill Mitty without making her suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be one somewhere out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sparagmos".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The "light that returns to the cardinal point."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a certain Relic that he called that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:19:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One of Mitty's eyes was squashed by it,\Nand that's the only part of her that doesn't regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Any spot it hits disappears\Nas if it's completely come undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately afterward,\Nthe surrounding air burns up to nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like the Incinerator!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to use it... then Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Mitty truly lost her humanity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She responds to people calling her, and-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I tried, real communication\Nbetween us proved impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so... her eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've seen it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I have a feeling that Mitty's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that Mitty's soul is imprisoned within that body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,give me some time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanachi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to do something\Nstrange like that outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll still keep treating Riko either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty's really taken a liking to her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of you as being so dependable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,just now you appeared so fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The vast amount of medicines here...\Nand the poisons, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,all of them are for the purpose\Nof trying to restore Mitty's dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is your very reason for living...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,after I have killed Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,what... what will become of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... just how many days\Nhave you been feeling down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make ya something really hearty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.29,0:21:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna have some shroom-bear meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be another one of Nanachi's dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi mixes everything way too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta bring out the best of the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you really suck at skinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go and take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat is really quite dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and it stinks, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember right, Riko did something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Were the innards supposed to come first?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Something ripped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This here... am I supposed to rinse it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doesn't this smell, like, super bad to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is worse than the stuff I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of excrement is filling my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, go on and call it irredeemable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irredeemable!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Before anyone knows it,\Nthe shooting stone leaves a trail,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,which falls as red-hot iron rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The ice-covered trees\Nproceed to transform into clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the gap in the sky,\Na large turtle with its neck stretched out is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please kill Mitty for me"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, Nanachi hasn't\Napproached me about it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to just leave things as they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.71,0:24:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, allow me to ask just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mitty unhappy being together with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.71,0:24:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I really don't think-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking that,\N"She seems to be living so peacefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so is it really necessary to kill her," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.71,0:24:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself will die somehow or other one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.25,0:24:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.92,0:24:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty will be all alone for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.63,0:24:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Mitty never eats and she still doesn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she gets stabbed, it still hurts her...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.46,0:24:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and she even sheds tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.67,0:25:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if those are mere reflexes,\Nshe'd still be forced to continue suffering forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.17,0:25:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not even capable of screaming out,\Nand yet her soul would remain imprisoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.33,0:25:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,eternally.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.38,0:25:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, this is the last chance for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.96,0:25:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can set Mitty free.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.71,0:25:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our last.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.04,0:25:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.50,0:25:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An opportunity like this won't ever present itself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.58,0:25:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.75,0:25:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, promise me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.13,0:25:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Mitty isn't around anymore,\Ndon't take your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.25,0:25:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still gotta take care of Riko... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.54,0:25:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after you're done treating Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.75,0:25:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.13,0:25:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.38,0:26:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.46,0:26:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.08,0:26:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With every ounce of my thoughts and feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will send her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.33,0:26:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.21,0:26:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you stick around here\Nwith me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.25,0:26:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be long before we can meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.67,0:26:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.75,0:27:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.42,0:27:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.00,0:27:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.08,0:27:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.50,0:27:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so, so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.46,0:27:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always, always be together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.04,0:27:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, you're so warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.08,0:27:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.58,0:28:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.08,0:28:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.83,0:29:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.75,0:29:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My... treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.79,0:29:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C-cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.17,0:30:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, this is no time to be feeling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.42,0:30:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.13,0:30:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.08,0:30:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you need to eat too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.50,0:30:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.04,0:30:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're done eating, we're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.79,0:30:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that odd smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.42,0:30:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.83,0:30:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're adapting way better than I could've ever imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.13,0:30:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, you're good at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.17,0:30:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.67,0:30:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.54,0:30:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.00,0:30:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.58,0:31:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.63,0:31:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she's still recovering, I thought I'd make her\Na stew that's nice and easy to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.92,0:31:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but she kept finding fault\Nwith the way I was preparing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.83,0:31:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what that odd smell was...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.63,0:31:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remove the entrails, it's gonna taste bland, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.96,0:31:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.63,0:31:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see demonfish also inhabit the fourth layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.42,0:31:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. That's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now carefully take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.79,0:31:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, you're good with your hands, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.75,0:31:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. Now you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.38,0:31:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't just stand there, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.13,0:31:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been like this since she first saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.17,0:31:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why you acting like you wanna rub me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.79,0:31:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, you don't seem to be hating it\Nas much as when I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.50,0:31:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.04,0:31:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you rub me in a lewd kinda way, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.67,0:31:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.21,0:32:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the bottom line's the taste. The taste, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.13,0:32:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.88,0:32:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... It was alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.46,0:32:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.67,0:32:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.29,0:32:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.50,0:32:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The eggs are yummy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.25,0:32:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Try one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.50,0:32:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wasn't there someone else here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.67,0:33:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.67,0:33:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.58,0:33:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why did I think that, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.29,0:33:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.79,0:33:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, I had this terribly frightening dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.04,0:33:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember it all that well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.04,0:33:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when I came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.63,0:33:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I found myself inside this pitch-black boulder-like thing\Nthat was horribly heavy and wouldn't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.79,0:33:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, there was this cavity inside it\Nthat was about the same size as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.42,0:33:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but it kept getting smaller and smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.83,0:33:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so painful, so agonizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.96,0:33:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even understand what I was anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.83,0:33:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I even forgot how to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.42,0:33:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared - so scared - and I just kept crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.88,0:34:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I heard crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.25,0:34:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But this crying wasn't coming from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.25,0:34:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I was startled...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.92,0:34:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I realized that the other girl was afraid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.92,0:34:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That helped ease my mind, if just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.42,0:34:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you see, I stayed like that for quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.13,0:34:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I got scared, there was this girl\Nright in front of me who was surely even more frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.96,0:34:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't speak, but with my eyes alone\NI kept on telling her, "It'll be alright, it'll be alright..."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.88,0:34:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I smelled something like smoke,\Nand the crying stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.67,0:34:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that girl simply left\Nwithout ever turning to look back...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.08,0:34:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could see her profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.00,0:34:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was just like all of the cave raiders I've seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.67,0:35:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That eye I saw was filled with longing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.63,0:35:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I remembered what it was\NI wanted to be one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.17,0:35:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "I need to get going"...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.38,0:35:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, I had a feeling I'd see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.88,0:35:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.25,0:35:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, Riko once...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.83,0:35:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko died once when she was a baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.58,0:35:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and was brought back to life again\Nby the power of a Relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.88,0:35:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko's life may very well be deeply tied to the Abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.96,0:35:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg... it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.83,0:35:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna head out for a bit to fetch some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.92,0:35:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, make sure you really protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.29,0:36:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.33,0:36:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.58,0:36:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.71,0:36:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I come to this same place when I'm injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.04,0:36:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.13,0:36:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange beasts that I've never seen anywhere else\Nalso come here to take a dip.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.21,0:36:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure this place is alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.67,0:36:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're docile to the point you can even pat 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.79,0:36:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The deep spots can be overly stimulating,\Nso stay outta 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.08,0:36:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's light coming up from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.63,0:36:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, sorry, but I can't get this off by myself.\NGive me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.54,0:36:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, lift your arm a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.83,0:36:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Reg, you wanna go in with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.29,0:36:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm just gonna keep a lookout, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.83,0:37:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.88,0:37:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes blood-sucking insects\Ncome to have a bite...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.96,0:37:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're pretty good at shooing those away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.58,0:37:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take lookout duty myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.33,0:37:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.29,0:37:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the bottom seems pretty slippery...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.17,0:37:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.13,0:37:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever we go, the color dissipates around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.04,0:37:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.38,0:37:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the water's hot,\Nthere are small fish in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.63,0:37:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish are eating the dead skin that's floating up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.88,0:37:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason... I feel thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.04,0:37:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! O-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.58,0:37:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?!\NOuch! O-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.25,0:37:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.38,0:37:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.38,0:37:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The hot water just stung a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.13,0:37:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.25,0:37:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.13,0:37:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.25,0:37:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with your penis?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.38,0:37:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.71,0:37:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.29,0:38:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.38,0:38:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,irredeemable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.58,0:38:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.67,0:38:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really still that fickle about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.79,0:38:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, come on, you've already kissed her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.21,0:38:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.29,0:38:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in acting embarrassed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.67,0:38:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, what's this kiss thing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.88,0:38:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.58,0:38:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was hardly a kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.46,0:38:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, how cowardly! You get in here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.50,0:38:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.67,0:38:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on lookout duty here,\Nso go ahead and take your time in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.96,0:38:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.96,0:38:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.13,0:38:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I can't bear to watch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.17,0:38:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.38,0:38:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You pulled Reg's treasure up outta that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.54,0:38:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.88,0:38:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you can wait for me just a bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.33,0:39:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.67,0:39:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Five more left!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.58,0:39:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A big central one comes next. Hold her down tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.46,0:39:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the thumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's the thumb alone, at least it moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.29,0:39:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.38,0:39:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.79,0:39:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I did such a bad job making the cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.58,0:39:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,your arm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.08,0:40:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, I'm the one who asked you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.54,0:40:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.63,0:40:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, it was Nanachi who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.88,0:40:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.67,0:40:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Told me that while you were working to save me, Reg,\Nyou were crying the whole time and were very worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.96,0:40:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I also heard that upon seeing you like that,\NNanachi thought, "That's me right there,"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.00,0:40:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and rushed to save me without so much as a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.83,0:40:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg... this scar is proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.88,0:40:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Precious proof that you protected me, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.08,0:40:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.58,0:40:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.92,0:40:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.29,0:40:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.67,0:40:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.00,0:40:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.38,0:41:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.50,0:41:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.04,0:41:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you consider coming along with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.04,0:41:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.00,0:41:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.17,0:41:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, I'm so happy! You're really okay with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.08,0:41:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.54,0:41:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.96,0:41:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.21,0:41:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well... Mitty did take a real liking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.21,0:41:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I abandoned you midway through your journey,\Nshe'd be mad at me next time we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.33,0:41:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't rely on just Reg alone, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.58,0:41:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.00,0:41:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not forget that Riko's cooking\Nis also really good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.25,0:41:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.54,0:41:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.92,0:41:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.38,0:41:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you the full story in due time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.46,0:41:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I came from the place that you're heading for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.00,0:41:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... the one you mentioned earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.08,0:41:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "in due time."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.29,0:41:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.38,0:42:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get started with the preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.58,0:42:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got quite a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.88,0:42:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna get going as soon as we can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.17,0:42:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.42,0:42:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is waiting for me, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.67,0:46:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.46,0:46:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.63,0:46:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.25,0:46:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.46,0:47:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see her signature has disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.58,0:47:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.46,0:47:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally managed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.96,0:47:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to express the extent of my gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.54,0:47:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I would very much like to see you again...
